WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.266 --> 00:00:04.700
Mr. Li, I went to investigate the surveillance at the scene of the incident

2
00:00:04.700 --> 00:00:05.866
But it was destroyed.

3
00:00:05.866 --> 00:00:07.366
I have contacted the technical department.

4
00:00:07.366 --> 00:00:08.400
Restore ASAP.

5
00:00:08.666 --> 00:00:10.666
How long at least three days

6
00:00:10.866 --> 00:00:13.366
Three days. I don't have that much time.

7
00:00:13.466 --> 00:00:14.766
I want results tonight

8
00:00:15.166 --> 00:00:16.300
Get out when it's repaired

9
00:00:16.533 --> 00:00:18.600
I'll get the tech department to step up

10
00:00:24.733 --> 00:00:25.533
Hello

11
00:00:27.666 --> 00:00:28.500
What!

12
00:00:29.533 --> 00:00:33.600
The people from Mr. Li's detention center said that his wife was missing

13
00:00:33.933 --> 00:00:35.000
Pardon me?

14
00:00:37.766 --> 00:00:39.700
Doctor, when can he write?

15
00:00:40.066 --> 00:00:42.166
It depends on his own will to survive

16
00:00:50.400 --> 00:00:52.400
Ah wake up

17
00:00:56.566 --> 00:00:57.366
Ziyu

18
00:00:58.933 --> 00:01:00.200
What are you doing here?

19
00:01:00.766 --> 00:01:02.500
Didn't you go to jail?

20
00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:05.466
My dad is at the top of the History Corporation

21
00:01:05.666 --> 00:01:07.433
How could I go to jail so easily?

22
00:01:08.566 --> 00:01:10.000
What have you done to me?

23
00:01:10.100 --> 00:01:13.633
Hey, I'm your savior now

24
00:01:14.266 --> 00:01:16.100
What can I do to you?

25
00:01:17.600 --> 00:01:19.633
You saved my life.

26
00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:23.266
Six months ago, Song Jixue sent someone to beat you into a vegetable

27
00:01:23.266 --> 00:01:25.333
I spent a lot of money and effort

28
00:01:25.333 --> 00:01:26.733
Just rescued you

29
00:01:26.733 --> 00:01:29.600
Am I not your savior?

30
00:01:30.266 --> 00:01:31.433
Has passed

31
00:01:32.066 --> 00:01:33.166
Has it been half a year?

32
00:01:33.166 --> 00:01:35.166
Yeah, half a year ago

33
00:01:35.166 --> 00:01:37.600
Song Jixue had already moved into Li's villa

34
00:01:37.700 --> 00:01:40.000
He also gave birth to a son for Libei Hyun

35
00:01:40.166 --> 00:01:41.900
After this month?

36
00:01:42.100 --> 00:01:42.700
Li Beixian

37
00:01:42.700 --> 00:01:45.000
They're going to have a feast for their son.

38
00:01:45.933 --> 00:01:47.433
Are you reconciled?

